{"tid":470062,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：游BB邀出戰九西　區諾軒說不 - 李八方","createTime":"2017-11-16T02:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T16:09:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58829350e5eab90c4c01ed9445503db0fd96864a","tid":470062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171116/20216148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F20216148&d=HEhLnMtwE8kNTIt9u6ef2DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e85391da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F20216148&h=c407e9d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171116/20216148</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：游BB邀出戰九西　區諾軒說不 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171116/large/18322299.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F18322299.jpg&h=96eb9908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區諾軒 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n九龍西、新界東補選七國咁亂，聽聞青年新政游蕙禎近排接觸過已退出民主黨嘅南區區議員區諾軒，問吓由佢出戰九西補選有冇得諗。區諾軒話，佢自己真係冇咩意願出戰，又話自己同九西就係好唔關事，所以唔好搞佢嘞。<br />\n<br />\n不過，民主派喺兩區補選嘅出戰陣容，好快就會明朗化，因為嚟緊呢個星期六，各有意出選嘅政團，都要向民主動力表明參選意向，組織派出嘅具體人選可容後交代。九西方面，參加組織要畀5至6萬元搞初選，新東方面，因為幅員較大，參加組織要畀約10萬元出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n民主動力召集人趙家賢話，希望下周可向外交代民主派整場補選嘅細節，佢話，𠵱家民主動力仲係相當努力咁協調各持份者嘅關注，希望搞好呢場初選。兩區補選，民主派之間咁多利害關係，八方就話由本身係調解員嘅趙家賢做統籌就最啱。"},{"pid":"79ae931da3b6a880534c5b91f8805f555cebb454","tid":470062,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:31:20.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"506c8dd9b2efac90e9e3bbf707775ad9e79c9005","tid":470062,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"條友話青年新政叫雞黨已經犯下不共戴天之仇啦"},{"pid":"dba79d609b98416e2783939193f91765f0f415bc","tid":470062,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:32:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fd72de58985841ebf30e71fae27caf447c1e4e6","tid":470062,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:56:16.000Z","msg":"廢游真係知錯嘅話就誠心向教主佢老人家道歉說服佢出山"},{"pid":"270807827dd888275ea4454e9037373af48bd17d","tid":470062,"uid":34377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢游真係知錯嘅話就誠心向教主佢老人家道歉說服佢出山</blockquote><br />\n係都熱狗班友道歉啦"},{"pid":"69fb6755841f9fe997edd2ed60be07c0652a9fac","tid":470062,"uid":34867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢游真係知錯嘅話就誠心向教主佢老人家道歉說服佢出山</blockquote><br />\n你on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}